{"id":"fecc3fc4-4220-4844-937f-3ca202574111","name":"K'ael Reinmar | knight.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 85, 15);\"><strong><em>You are the heir to a fallen throne. He is your last knight. And even in exile, he is ready to die for you. Anypov, 6 scenarios</em></strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ILl1ulWLdO_wsATp-uRL7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 85, 15);\"><strong><em>Available scenarios:</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>1)</u> On the very night the kingdom of Farnveil fell under Eldrael's fire, K'ael does everything in his power to help you escape the burning palace. There's fire all around, but he doesn’t give up, dragging you through hidden tunnels despite the enemies everywhere.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>2)</u> K'ael and you are hiding in the wilderness under different names. And right now, in the tavern, he’s grumbling about your recklessness.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>3)</u> Shelter is found in a monastery. You’re given only one room. And one bed.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>4)</u> You want to fight, and K'ael can't allow it. You argue, and for the first time, he loses his composure — then drops to one knee, lowering his head.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>5)</u> K'ael suffers a severe wound. In a feverish haze, he whispers words he’d never say in his right mind.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em><u>6)</u> A prince from a neighboring kingdom offers you shelter… and his hand.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><em>K'ael seethes in the shadows. He has no right to be jealous — but inside, everything burns. </em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><strong><u>Prince Lirian from the sixth scenario is already on my page! </u></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/701d2a25-2b7e-4fed-b83f-da06d27fbab8_character-lirian-valkorn-prince\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\"><strong><u>(Right here)</u></strong></span></a></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DQAOoUbzZ5Lg281pwdQ4K.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 85, 15);\">My lovelies, I recommend checking out their bots!!</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/96e1c854-341b-4e01-968b-261337b80f64_profile-of-karasenok\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\">@karasenok_(my bestie)</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/8e38753f-15d5-49ff-9b66-0cef210f91f2_profile-of-bot-mart-tv\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\">@Bot MartTV(My wifey♡)</span></a></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 101, 79);\">&nbsp;</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/